title: "Fast Times at Ridgemont High"
rating: 6.7
review {
  direction {
    director {
      name: "Amy Heckerling"
    }
    rating: "Decent to Pretty Good"
    comments: "The direction on a macroscale is very high-school, hangout movie-esque as she does a decent job at building the world; the direction on a microscale is pretty good as the scenes are memorable, but still what you would expect from younger actors; the storytelling is very linear and on-par with other teen movies"
