  story {
    writer {
      name: "Cameron Crowe"
    }
    rating: "Decent"
    comments: "The concept is typical of other high school movies, but has more of a hang-out feel as we go through the different storylines; the plot structure is a little non-traditional as we go through multiple storylines that are running in parallel, with some intersections; character writing is pretty standard for a high school movie, though it does create some iconic characters"
  }
